uote-contentid=\u0022219269\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221693884513\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Anth12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Anth12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChanged the title to add the toggle aspect\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI took\u00A0 Spaceman42069\u0027s:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Center of Mass widget does not update until you toggle it off and on\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nto mean the same as Moredice\u0027s:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00225. Either disable and enable \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECoM\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E indication again...\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I am dyslexic as **** so I could be wrong about that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-05T03:48:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are related. I will have to figure out a better title.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-05T03:58:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/210559-naughtymonster/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022210559\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/210559-naughtymonster/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@NaughtyMonster\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/229539-moredice/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022229539\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/229539-moredice/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Moredice\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/230465-spaceman42069/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022230465\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/230465-spaceman42069/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@spaceman42069\u003C/a\u003E Changed title to add the other bug report and have it make sense being merged. Makes sense now?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Moredice","CreatedById":229539,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-05T22:04:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/161238-anth12/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161238\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/161238-anth12/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Anth12\u003C/a\u003E Looks good to me!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kr0meel","CreatedById":231146,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-05T13:16:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.5 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Intel(R) Core(TM) i5-9600K | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA RTX3080 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E16 GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn an airplane configuration, where fuel tanks are stacked horizontally I would expect the Center of Gravity marker to move forward or backwards if the contents of one of the tanks is changed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExample:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoad the default \u0022Aeris-K2\u0022 airplane:\u00A0 it has 2 JF-200 methane tanks, with each 2 tons of fuel in them.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen the engineering report: the plane has a total mass of 7.7 tons, and a dry mass of 3.57\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nEnable the COG marker: notice how\u00A0it lies somewhere in the front tank.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nChange the contents of the rear tank from 2 tons to zero, in the engineering report the total mass is\u00A0immediately updated to 5.7 tons (which seems correct)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nNotice however that the COG marker doesn\u0027t move at all, while it should definitely move forward:\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThese 2 tons are\u00A0a significant part of the total mass of this plane\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe removed mass lies at a significant distance behind the original COG.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTurning the COG marker off and on again updates the marker position to what seems to be the correct location.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-11-05T13:37:06Z\u0022 title=\u002211/05/2023 01:37  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Nov 5\u0022\u003ENovember 5, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-29T02:38:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Phenom(tm) II X6 1055T Processor 2.80 GHz | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2070 SUPER | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E24.0 GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Center of mass marker turned on for a rocket stage.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022QNOSraq.jpg\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/QNOSraq.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Drain/change fuel values for that stage using the part manager. \u003Cstrong\u003EThe center of mass marker doesn\u0027t move to the proper location on its own as you do that.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jP9q9ec.jpg\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/jP9q9ec.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. To get the center of mass to take on its proper location again, you have to click its button twice to make it disappear and reappear in the new location.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022J7UfhOf.jpg\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/J7UfhOf.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022em22LHQ.jpg\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/em22LHQ.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-30T00:19:42Z\u0022 title=\u002212/30/2023 12:19  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 30\u0022\u003EDecember 30, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Peacock","CreatedById":224498,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-30T03:41:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/229539-moredice/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022229539\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/229539-moredice/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Moredice\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0moved this report out of the archive\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/150330-cubinator/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022150330\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/150330-cubinator/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@cubinator\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0merged your report\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-31T12:52:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231146-kr0meel/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022231146\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231146-kr0meel/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kr0meel\u003C/a\u003E, merged your bug report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wuschelfun","CreatedById":232083,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-07T18:20:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 5 7600X | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2060 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32 GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\